                     <a id="a071200"></a>
                     <div class="entry" id="entry-71200">
                        <h1 class="entry-header"><a href="http://www.treehugger.com/files/2011/06/magi-cam-uses-mirror-covered-robot-to-record-camera-shy-animals.php">"Magi-Cam" Uses Mirror-Covered Robot to Record Camera-Shy Animals (Video)</a></h1>
                     <h5 class="tagline">by <a href="http://www.treehugger.com/author/jaymi-heimbuch-san-francisco-c-1/">Jaymi Heimbuch, San Francisco, California</a> <a href="http://www.treehugger.com/feeds/authors/jaymi.xml"><img style="margin-bottom: -1px;" src="http://www.treehugger.com/images_site/feed-icon-10x10.png" /></a> on  	06.22.11</h5>
                        <div class="entry-content">
                           <div class="entry-body">
                              <div class="cat-indicator">

<a href="http://www.treehugger.com/science_technology/">Science & Technology</a>
<br>

<!-- Begin Social Media Widgets -->
